[SN]TITLE[SN]
In Pictures: Wales takes major step towards Euro 2016 with 1-0 win

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Wales has claimed a momentous win against Belgium at Cardiff City Stadium to regain top spot in their Euro 2016 qualifying group.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The win has brought the team closer to ending their 57-year absence from major tournaments.
Gareth Bale scored the winner on his 50th Wales appearance.
It was the first defeat for Belgium since the 2014 World Cup.
